THE GAME
--------

  'Ixo' is a Workbench game where you place coloured bars in an
8 by 8 spaces game board. The idea is to create alignments of 8
horizontal bars in a row or 8 vertical bars in a column. If the
alignments have bars of the same colour and none of them are
crossing other bars, the better it is...

  However, watch out for the 'ClickoMeter', what's that? It is a
display which shows how many times you can click on the game board
to place bars... when it has reached its limit, the game is
over...

  Have fun!

